{"TopicId":172691,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Uber Troubles For Uber","CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-20T00:28:42Z","PageNum":10,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T18:19:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223373993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172691\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525799425\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSelf driving cars are not AGI, nor sentient, and won\u0027t ever be. Driving is a mechanical task that requires neither capability.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... evidenced by some of the human drivers on the road\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_blink.png\u0022 title=\u0022:blink:\u0022\u003E. If autonomous vehicles didn\u2019t\u00A0have to be concerned about unpredictable meatbags, they would be easy to develop with modern tech, especially if the roads were built for them (electronic lane markers embedded in the road surface).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T18:22:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyone who touches their phone while driving is already acting as if we have self-driving vehicles. Any \u003Cem\u003Eactual\u003C/em\u003E self-driving can only be an improvement, IMHO.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T20:43:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223374043\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172691\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525803553\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nroads were built for them (electronic lane markers embedded in the road surface)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean just like the robot pallet drivers used in the manufacturing warehouse. They\u0027re not infallible either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T00:09:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223373993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172691\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525799425\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDriving\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E is a mechanical task that requires neither capability.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI invite you to drive in my country. See how far that philosophy stands.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T01:46:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223374308\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172691\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525824556\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002298447\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022YNM\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, YNM said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI invite you to drive in my country. See how far that philosophy stands.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne, I only care about self driving vehicles here, where I will use or interact with them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTwo, it is true, regardless. If they can identify and negotiate a world with pedestrians, cyclists, pets, etc, it should generalize well enough.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T01:57:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223374352\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172691\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525830369\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E, I only \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ecare about self driving vehicles here, where I will use or interact with them.\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, so much about that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022te-sundaytimes.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022372\u0022 src=\u0022http://cbrd.co.uk/sites/default/files/ringways/background/te-sundaytimes.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tater","CreatedById":119411,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T04:03:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAutonomous cars will end up saving vast numbers of lives. People were afraid of elevators without human operators at first as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe metric is only to be safer than human drivers, and humans are awful drivers, and are getting worse, not better. The only reason safety is better is car design, and trauma care. I see distracted (phones) drivers virtually constantly. A substantial fraction of motorists have phones out at any given time. I am confident that a short trip to the grocery store involves passing double digit numbers of cars with drivers texting, etc (both directions, so largely closing cars).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe sooner those people are not driving, the better.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-09T09:59:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223374406\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172691\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525838606\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022119411\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tater\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, tater said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E sooner \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Ethose people are not driving, the better\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E.\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. But also remove the cars.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/jcREB7zkjj4?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/3g-z-PEzTas?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/_DNNIB_PdaA?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-09T12:09:39Z\u0022 title=\u002205/09/2018 12:09  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 9, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by YNM\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-10T18:14:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou know, the solution to all of this is to genetically re-engineer people and give them wings.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}